width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I do tend to get hangry more often than I'd like</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gTQ5AhQ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>You can tell it's a Dad joke, because it's apparent.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BGMW0vG.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>These are pretty tasty, actually</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/NUQuyxB.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>DANGIT, BOB</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/MCl14vJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The glasses totally hide him tho</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/IdC1J7U.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>RONNY IS GOOD DOG, BRONT</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/49cDt69.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>They smell nice for a little while too</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PgU114b.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Intrusive thoughts better stay out</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0REPxOJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Is that a giant frog on a normal-sized unicorn? Or a normal-sized frog on a tiny unicorn? WE MAY NEVER KNOW</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/nSnlvVk.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I can see myself buying one someday, tho</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0NmyFEG.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>WHOOOAAAAA MANNNNNN</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/puKdej3.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Soft kitty, warm kitty, little ball of furrrrrr</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/SkEY64R.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>JESUS AND AMMO</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JSitYOk.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>My dad was after me to be a doctor too. I'M AN ARTEEST</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/k48SCA5.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Them Ls are stacking up</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/V2UuT8s.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Like, ALL of them, because, y'know... science.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/UBk2444.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Made me feel Dopey too</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/aBxZBTZ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>He looks nice</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/r4xphEf.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Poor Snail</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6ZCGh2D.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Spine is shaped like a big ol' question mark</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/oUCjGAX.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I'd watch it</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gTNzeT1.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>His money just grows on trees</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3dS7eb0.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I ran into this last week. I just said "Ha, you win the lottery of standing exactly where I need to go, ha! Let me squeeze in there, 'scuse  me..."</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/f19v2Yh.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Every single time. If it's not bird poo, it's rain the very next day.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gNCn5lO.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Blue is Bad, Red is Rad, right?</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tRETFl8.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>King's Hawaiian actually does make hotdog buns too, they're tasty</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/nM6FJVL.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>here ya go</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1yJsX2z.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>yeah, Pot Temperatures are a hoax</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/cZkgfM0.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Do something you love, and you'll never work a day in your life</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Vys3a3Z</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ddubya42]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>We could be heroes</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/AyjbrTa</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/nJJE0yZ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/AyjbrTa</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[VelvetWarhol]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Return of the Meme: 1275 (LOTR sunday)</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/K61ihXh</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4afT4yv.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Let's get this lembas.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/17SEDVc.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Hey!  If you're a woman or minority in a STEM field in Arizona living north of Phoenix and you need new headshots for this website or an